<p>I'd say get rid of the &quot;addendum&quot; altogether in the containment. It's just far too lolfoundation for this day and age, and i would think that would be an &quot;update&quot; not an &quot;addendum&quot;.</p>
<p>I love the thing itself, though. Like, all over it.</p>
<p>The final addendum seems a bit&#8230; Eh, however. The Guardians of Light sounds like a good &quot;fringe group&quot; but all those names? The morning star, the lightbringer? Those are terms/titles typically used in pre-fall <strong>Lucifer</strong>. Not sure if that was intentional or not. Bonus points if these guys are <em>accidentally</em> worshiping Satan (or an analogue) or are pulling the whole &quot;God is evil / Satan is good&quot; trope.</p>
<p>Also not finding the Easter egg you're claiming, unless I'm being obtuse, or not remembering something else you did was actually yours.</p>

